<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re,</expan> uns <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> fürgelegt
                                <expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Rumell, Cristan Haller und Conrad
